(60, 1, '2015-06-08 16:46:12', '2015-06-08 16:46:12', 'Alhumdulillah, Masjid Suffah has now been open for over two months. In this time, we have been blessed with a positive response from the community. We have an active group of members who join us for the 5 daily salah and nearly 125 community members in attendance for Jummah. We have also been able to launch several programs, including summer classes for children, Friday family halaqahs, and a daily hadith halaqah.\r\n\r\nThe fruits of the community\'s efforts have certainly paid off. In fact, last Jummah, Brother Brandon Alexander accepted Islam. Please help us give him a warm welcome to the community.\r\n\r\nBecause we have had a greater response from the community than we had initially anticipated, the masjid has begun to undergo construction for expansion. We anticipate completing the expansion before the beginning of Ramadan, which will include larger prayer areas for both the men and women and a proper wudhu area, inshaAllah.\r\n\r\nWe would like to thank the community for all of their efforts and for helping to make our vision of a vibrant masjid in Kennesaw possible.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to seeing everyone during the upcoming blessed month of Ramadan!', 'Overwhelming Community Response Warrants Masjid Expansion', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-08 16:46:12', '2015-06-08 16:46:12', '', 1, 'http://www.masjidsuffah.com/uncategorized/1-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2015-06-08 16:50:06', '2015-06-08 16:50:06', '[et_pb_section fullwidth=\"on\" specialty=\"off\"][et_pb_fullwidth_slider admin_label=\"Fullwidth Slider\" show_arrows=\"on\" show_pagination=\"on\" auto=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\"][et_pb_slide heading=\"About Masjid Suffah\" background_image=\"http://www.masjidsuffah.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/headerimage2.jpg\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" alignment=\"center\" background_layout=\"dark\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" /][/et_pb_fullwidth_slider][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n<h1>Educate. Cultivate. Serve.</h1>\r\nMasjid Suffah is a non-profit religious organization established in 2015 to provide a place of worship for Muslims residing in and around Kennesaw.\r\n\r\nMasjid Suffah is named after the Ashab al-Suffah, the People of the Porch. The Ashab al-Suffah were a group of companions of the Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) who sat on the porch of the masjid (mosque). They devoted their lives to studying Islam. Learning at the feet of the Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) allowed the People of the Porch to cultivate a deep understanding of Islam within themselves, which allowed them to serve Allah and serve the community at large. At Masjid Suffah, we hope to revive the spirit of the Ashab al-Suffah through education, cultivation, and service.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.masjidsuffah.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/vision.jpg\" alt=\"Vision of Masjid Suffah serving the Kennesaw muslim community\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"fade_in\" sticky=\"off\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]We want to be a vibrant faith community that appreciates the inherent worth of every individual. Organized and fully supported by all stakeholders, operation with the highest level of Shura (consultation). we envisioned ourselves a role model 21st century Masjid, which will be the center of learning for the local as well as global communities. With the support of our thriving business community, we are positioned for growth and expansion. A state-of-the-art, green and financially solvent community will nurture Islamic culture and business while fulfilling the destiny of a God-conscious community.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.masjidsuffah.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/mission.jpg\" alt=\"Vision of Masjid Suffah serving the Kennesaw muslim community\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"fade_in\" sticky=\"off\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]The Suffa Dawat Center in Kennesaw would be committed to the Islamic way of life based on the Quran and the life example (Sunnah) of the Prophet Muhammad (pbuh). We shall strive to serve as a center for religious development, social, educational, economic and cultural enrichment. We believe in the oneness of Allah and the oneness of humanity. We are committed to promoting excellence in community life and human dignity throughout our neighborhoods in general and particularly in the city of Kennesaw by promoting the real essence of Islam.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-08 16:50:06', '2015-06-08 16:50:06', '', 2, 'http://www.masjidsuffah.com/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
