(102, 1, '2015-06-16 15:40:45', '2015-06-16 15:40:45', 'As-salamu alaykum,\r\n\r\nThe Masjid Suffah board will meet on Wednesday, June 17, 2015 (Shaban 29, 1436) to determine the start of Ramadan. If the moon is seen on Wednesday, June 17th, Ramadan will begin on Thursday, June 18th and <em>taraweeh</em> prayers will begin Wednesday June 17th after isha (10:30pm). If the moon is not seen on Wednesday, June 17th, Ramadan will begin on Friday, June 19th.\r\n\r\nAccording to visibility forecasts, the moon should be visible in the lower parts of North America on Wednesday, June 17th. Hence, Ramadan will most likely begin on Thursday, June 18th. InshaAllah the board will be sighting the moon locally (anywhere in NA and SA) using the following hilal committees:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>New York Hilal Committee: <a href=\"http://www.hilalcommittee.org/\">http://www.hilalcommittee.org/</a></li>\r\n	<li>Toronto Hilal Committee: <a href=\"http://www.hilalcommittee.com/\">http://www.hilalcommittee.com/</a></li>\r\n	<li>Chicago Hilal Committee: <a href=\"http://chicagohilal.org/\">http://chicagohilal.org/</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Masjid Suffah Ramadan Iftar Program:</strong> This includes the dates, dinner, supplies, cleaning etc. Please participate in this program by contributing in any way possible. We schedule dinner donations to avoid overlapping, and provide balance, so please contact us to book a date in advance.\r\n\r\n<strong>ALL CHICKEN &amp; MEAT MUST BE HAND ZABIHA.</strong>\r\n\r\nYou can contribute to this program in several ways:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Provide cooked dinners. Please contact us to schedule these!</li>\r\n	<li>Contribute cash to purchase supplies (plates, cups, spoons, napkins, or dates).</li>\r\n	<li>Bring dates, fruits or bottled water.</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer to assist in daily set up, clean up, &amp; generally provide service to others.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nMay Allah SWT reward us all bountifully, as we seek His pleasure during this blessed month.\r\n\r\nTo donate, schedule dinners, or contribute in any way, please contact anyone on the Masjid Suffah board.', 'Ramadan Moon-Sighting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ramadan-moon-sighting', '', '', '2015-11-13 22:13:54', '2015-11-13 22:13:54', '', 0, 'http://www.masjidsuffah.com/?p=102', 0, 'post', '', 0),
