(192, 1, '2015-08-07 15:38:35', '2015-08-07 15:38:35', '<h1>Essentials of Islam</h1>\r\nAlhamdulillah, we are excited to announce that beginning on Tuesday, August 11, 2015 Masjid Suffah will be starting the inaugural Maktab/Evening Quran Class for children ages 6-15 years old. Throughout this school year, the students will be following an established curriculum based off of the Tasheel Series from South Africa and the Deeniyat Series from the subcontinent to learn subjects including, but not limited to: <strong><em>Tajweed</em></strong> (Quranic Pronunciation and Rules)<em>, <strong>Quran</strong></em>,<strong><em> Fiqh </em></strong>(Rules of Worship)<em>,<strong> Aqeedah </strong>(</em>Beliefs)<em>, <strong>Hadith</strong> </em>(Prophetic Sayings), <strong>Arabic Language</strong>, and <strong>Islamic History</strong>.\r\n\r\nClasses will be three days a week  Tuesday, Wednesday, and Thursday  from 5:30 pm  7:00 pm. Both boys and girls are welcome and will have separate teachers, who were born and raised in the USA.\r\n\r\nOn Tuesday (August 11<sup>th</sup>), we will, inshaAllah, have a registration day from 5:30-7:00 pm. <strong><u>All</u></strong> parents who intend to enroll their children must come to register. Please bring your children along with you, so the teachers will have an opportunity to meet them. Parents will also have an opportunity to speak with the administration and teachers about any questions or concerns they may have.\r\nWe look forward to seeing you on Tuesday!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.masjidsuffah.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Admissions-Form-2015.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Please click here for student registration form</a>', 'Masjid Suffah Maktab/Evening Quran Class for Children', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'masjid-suffah-maktabevening-quran-class-for-children', '', '', '2015-11-13 22:14:25', '2015-11-13 22:14:25', '', 0, 'http://www.masjidsuffah.com/?p=192', 0, 'post', '', 0),
