(215, 1, '2015-08-20 23:08:17', '2015-08-20 23:08:17', '<h2><strong><u>Arabic Classes for Men </u></strong></h2>\r\nAlhamdulillah, Masjid Suffah is happy to announce our newest program. Starting from next Saturday, August 29<sup>th</sup>, 2015, Masjid Suffah will be offering <strong><u>free</u></strong> Arabic classes for men on Saturdays from 12:45pm until Zuhr salah (2:00). Classes will be taught by brother Rabah. We thank Brother Rabah for volunteering to teach this class, and we ask that Allah Taala accepts his efforts and sincerity.\r\n\r\nDuring this class, we will have an opportunity to understand and learn to speak in the language of Rasulullah , the Quran, and the people of Jannah. Please take advantage of this opportunity to learn this beautiful language\r\n\r\nTo better prepare for the class, please complete the registration form by clicking on the link below. If more than one person is attending from a single family, please complete the registration form for each individual.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/forms/RwyR2FVbnA\">http://goo.gl/forms/RwyR2FVbnA</a>\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, please contact the Masjid Management by emailing us at suffahmasjid@gmail.com.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Free Arabic Classes', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'free-arabic-classes', '', '', '2015-11-22 23:45:18', '2015-11-22 23:45:18', '', 0, 'http://www.masjidsuffah.com/?p=215', 0, 'post', '', 0),
